            "answer_text": "Saying \u201ca retaliation\u201d or even \u201cthe retaliation\u201d is sometimes right, but it\u2019s more common to see the word \u201cretaliation\u201d used without an article, like \u201canger\u201d or \u201chunger.\u201d You would want to say either \u201cHe will do it in retaliation\u201d or \u201cas retaliation.\u201d \u201cIn\u201d or \u201cas,\u201d no \u201ca.\u201d ",
